    "description": "Path of Kingdoms is a strategy game where the player must defeat all the factions of the kingdom to reach the goal, each faction has a story that evolves as it conquers territories through narrated interlude scenes.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 6 different factions, each faction having completely different gameplay characteristics that make the gaming experience very different (not only the difficulty level).<br></li><li> Each faction's units have completely different characteristics such as endurance, speed, strength, etc..<br></li><li> Each battle, even if the scenery is similar, is unique: there are over 100 parameters that customise the combat environments: position and type of enemy units, weather, additional animals, wind, grass, stones... characteristics that change the combat strategy in each battle.<br></li><li> The evolution of the map, which adapts with the player, changes with each game.<br></li><li> Different combat units: light infantry, scouts, heavy infantry, cavalry, archers, sorcerers, catapults.<br></li><li> Different types of battle: kill enemies, liberate villages, besiege towns, defend villages, resist enemy assault, ...<br></li><li> Enemy AI that evolves with the player: prepare assaults, encirclement strategies, traps, ...</li></ul><br><strong>Battle Mode</strong>.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Kill all enemies<br></li><li> Clear territories<br></li><li> Kill all enemies in a preset time<br></li><li> Defend territories</li></ul>",
